post.title: Actual problems/limitations on ZeroNet we will laugh in future
post.body:
*   Need do tell user in another place that a ZeroMail message was sent/replied (no notifications working)
*   Need python script and CMS site to upload videos
*   Need external client to seed videos
*   Social medias can't have a "online users" feature, or it will flood the network

This list can increase. Please comment.

post.title: The computing/Internet is reseting
post.body:
A lot of things are evolving in the computing, and many of those evolutions are about how computing/Internet should be at the beginning.

See what is changing:

* Internet sites > ZeroNet
* Internet infraestructure > Mesh Networks
* BIOS > DCRS
* Operating system > Screens

Something to add or ask, please comment.

post.title: Projects to make a donation for
post.body:
Some gorgeous projects to make a donation for (they supports Bitcoin donation, and this list is growing):

- ZeroNet https://zeronet.readthedocs.io/en/latest/help_zeronet/donate/

- Tails (the privacy OS) https://tails.boum.org/donate/index.pt.html#sidebar

- Bitcoin Paper Wallet https://bitcoinpaperwallet.com/#donate

- Wikileaks https://shop.wikileaks.org/donate

- Tor https://donate.torproject.org

- Signal https://support.whispersystems.org/hc/en-us/articles/212940158-How-can-I-donate-

- Namecoin https://namecoin.org/donate/

Please help this list grow by commenting. I'll edit when I know more.
